{"tid":1430111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果71 無衝擊到立法會，而家個結果會係點？","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:12:19.000Z","uid":108203,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc64e848b5c151bfe6cd8b77d14a75fd7dc626a7","tid":1430111,"uid":108203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"因為71 有烈士不顧一切爆玻璃開始，一開始好多人鬧爆玻璃，但之後好多人先開始勇武衝擊，到而家爆玻璃已經係正常。<br />\n<br />\n如果立法會無破壞到，會議每星期如常繼續，每星期遊行變左圍立法會，因為而家無左立法會會議， 好多時先可以係7區進行， 唔洗下下出港島，仲會唔會有咁多人勇武"},{"pid":"c259fb28c4e3d7b982db0d1bd4e2e3d7c7a552e9","tid":1430111,"uid":102308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjcOpRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjcOpRk.jpg&h=4850de5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2VkfX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2VkfX0.jpg&h=3aceafd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VpnnupT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVpnnupT.png&h=bf703274&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea4a729ccffed4090992f6dc3145fe522d064eee","tid":1430111,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"連登封撚左啦"},{"pid":"11e4f3319ac99c15f68fd510d612e935a0966983","tid":1430111,"uid":108203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:10:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a8dea6355f6a6f1d545734654ec00a65d6c2e8e","tid":1430111,"uid":108203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}